2 Figure 3B


cd /data1/qtl/code_for_submit/data/Fig3B

vim GARFIELD.sh

# -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INPUTNAME=lung_cancer
DATADIR=/data1/qtl/3QTL/enrichment/gwas/garfield-data

PRUNETAGSDIR=$DATADIR/tags/new/r01
CLUMPTAGSDIR=$DATADIR/tags/new/r08
MAFTSSDDIR=$DATADIR/maftssd/new
PVALDIR=$DATADIR/pval/$INPUTNAME
ANNOTDIR=$DATADIR/lung_cancer_updated
OUTDIR=$DATADIR/output/update_$INPUTNAME/5e_04
mkdir -p $OUTDIR

ANNOTLINKFILE=$ANNOTDIR/link_file.txt
PTHRESH=5e-4
BINNING=m5,n5,t5
CONDITION=0
SUBSET="1-3"

F1=$OUTDIR/garfield.prep.$INPUTNAME.out
F0=$OUTDIR/garfield.Meff.$INPUTNAME.out

echo 'Prune and Clump'
echo -n > $F1
for CHR in `seq 1 22` 
do
echo 'CHR'$CHR
./garfield-prep-chr \
-ptags $PRUNETAGSDIR/chr$CHR \
-ctags $CLUMPTAGSDIR/chr$CHR \
-maftss $MAFTSSDDIR/chr$CHR \
-pval $PVALDIR/chr$CHR \
-ann $ANNOTDIR/chr$CHR \
-chr $CHR -o $F1 || { echo 'Failure!'; } 
done

echo 'Calculate effective number of annotations'
Rscript garfield-Meff-Padj.R -i $F1 -o $F0
NEA=$(head -1 $F0 |awk '{print $2}')
Padj=$(tail -1 $F0 |awk '{print $2}')

echo 'Calculate Enrichment and Significance'
F2=$OUTDIR/garfield.test.$INPUTNAME.out
Rscript garfield-test.R -i $F1 -o $F2 -l $ANNOTLINKFILE -pt $PTHRESH -b $BINNING -s $SUBSET -c $CONDITION
echo 'GARFIELD single annotation analysis complete'

# -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

chmod 777 GARFIELD.sh
sh GARFIELD.sh


# Plot
R
rm(list = ls())
library(data.table)
library(ggplot2)

list <- c('NSCLC','LUAD','LUSC')
eqtl <- data.frame()
for (i in 1:length(list)) {
  dat <- fread(paste0('eqtl/',list[i],'.garfield.test.lung_cancer.out'))
  dat$disease <- list[i]
  dat$QTL_type <- 'eQTL'
  dat$or <- exp(dat$Beta)
  dat$or_low_ci <- exp(dat$Beta-1.96*dat$SE)
  dat$or_upper_ci <- exp(dat$Beta+1.96*dat$SE)
  dat <- subset(dat,PThresh=='5e-04')
  eqtl <- rbind(eqtl,dat)
}

aqtl <- data.frame()
for (i in 1:length(list)) {
  dat <- fread(paste0('aqtl/',list[i],'.garfield.test.lung_cancer.out'))
  dat$disease <- list[i]
  dat$QTL_type <- 'apaQTL'
  dat$or <- exp(dat$Beta)
  dat$or_low_ci <- exp(dat$Beta-1.96*dat$SE)
  dat$or_upper_ci <- exp(dat$Beta+1.96*dat$SE)
  dat <- subset(dat,PThresh=='5e-04')
  aqtl <- rbind(aqtl,dat)
}

sqtl <- data.frame()
for (i in 1:length(list)) {
  dat <- fread(paste0('sqtl/',list[i],'.garfield.test.lung_cancer.out'))
  dat$disease <- list[i]
  dat$QTL_type <- 'sQTL'
  dat$or <- exp(dat$Beta)
  dat$or_low_ci <- exp(dat$Beta-1.96*dat$SE)
  dat$or_upper_ci <- exp(dat$Beta+1.96*dat$SE)
  dat <- subset(dat,PThresh=='5e-04')
  sqtl <- rbind(sqtl,dat)
}
data <- rbind(aqtl,eqtl,sqtl)
data$QTL_type <- factor(data$QTL_type,levels = c('apaQTL','eQTL','sQTL'))
data$disease <- factor(data$disease,levels = rev(c('NSCLC','LUAD','LUSC')))
data$signif <- ifelse(data$Pvalue < 0.001, "***", ifelse(data$Pvalue<0.01 & data$Pvalue>0.001, "**", ifelse(data$Pvalue<0.05,"*","")))

ggplot(data, aes(x = or, y = disease, color = QTL_type)) +
  geom_point(size = 2, position = position_dodge(width = 0.8)) +
  geom_errorbarh(aes(xmin = or_low_ci, xmax = or_upper_ci), linewidth = 0.75,height = 0.5, position = position_dodge(width = 0.8)) +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("apaQTL" = "#BC3C29", "eQTL" = "#2D417F", "sQTL" = "#CB812A")) +
  theme_classic(base_size = 14) +
  labs(x = "Enrichment estimate \n(log-odds ratio and 95% CI)", y = "", color = "") +
  theme(legend.position = "top",
    axis.text.y = element_text(size = 14,colour = 'black'),
    axis.text.x = element_text(size = 14,colour = 'black')) +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 1, linetype = "dashed", color = "grey50", linewidth = 1)+
  geom_text(aes(label = signif, x = or_upper_ci + 0.1), 
    position = position_dodge(width = 0.8),
    size = 6, hjust = 0,color = "black")

ggsave(file='Figure 3B.pdf',height = 4.5,width = 3.9)

library(data.table)
library(ggplot2)
rm(list = ls())
eQTL <- fread('338sample_eqtl.p0005.txt.gz')
aQTL <- fread('338sample_aqtl.p0005.txt.gz')
sQTL <- fread('338sample_sqtl.p0005.txt.gz')
names(eQTL) <- c('gene_id','variant_id','tss_distance','ma_samples','ma_count','maf','pval_nominal','slope','slope_se')
names(aQTL) <- c('gene_id','variant_id','tss_distance','ma_samples','ma_count','maf','pval_nominal','slope','slope_se')
names(sQTL) <- c('gene_id','variant_id','tss_distance','ma_samples','ma_count','maf','pval_nominal','slope','slope_se')
aQTL_lead <- aQTL
eQTL_lead <- eQTL
sQTL_lead <- sQTL
RA_gwas <-fread("../3_China_pop_NSCLC_updated_0916.TBL")
RA_gwas$aQTL <- RA_gwas$eQTL <- RA_gwas$sQTL <-  0
RA_gwas[which(RA_gwas$MarkerName %in% aQTL_lead$variant_id),"aQTL" ] <- 1
RA_gwas[which(RA_gwas$MarkerName %in% eQTL_lead$variant_id), "eQTL"] <- 1
RA_gwas[which(RA_gwas$MarkerName %in% sQTL_lead$variant_id), "sQTL"] <- 1
cbbPalette <- c( "#BC3C29","#2D417F", "#CB812A")
RA_p_values <- list('aQTL'=dplyr::filter(RA_gwas,aQTL==1)$`P-value`,
                    'eQTL'=dplyr::filter(RA_gwas,eQTL==1)$`P-value`,
                    'sQTL'=dplyr::filter(RA_gwas,sQTL==1)$`P-value`,
                    'NSCLC'=RA_gwas$`P-value`)

pdf(file = 'Figure 3B.pdf',width = 5,height = 4)
m6Amonster::qqplot.pvalue(RA_p_values,legendSize = 1.75)+
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 14,colour = "black"),
        axis.text =  element_text(size = 14,colour = "black"), 
        legend.title = element_blank(),
        legend.text =  element_text(size = 14,colour = "black"),
        axis.line = element_line(linewidth = 1) )+
  scale_color_manual(values = cbbPalette)
dev.off()

data <- fread('data.txt')
data$rowname <- paste0(data$disease,'_',data$type)
data <- as.matrix(data)
rownames(data) <- data[,6]
write.csv(data,file = 'res_num.csv',row.names = F)
mat <- as.matrix(apply(data[,3:5],2,as.numeric))
rownames(mat) <- rownames(data)

methods.col <- brewer.pal(n = length(unique(data[,1])),name = "Paired")
annColors <- list(QTLs = c("apaQTL" = "#CD534C", "eQTL" = "#7AA6DC","sQTL" = "#FFDC91"),Disease = c("NSCLC" = methods.col[2], "LUAD" = methods.col[1],"LUSC" = methods.col[3]))
annotation_row <- data.frame(QTLs = factor(data[,2], levels = c('apaQTL','eQTL','sQTL')),Disease = factor(data[,1], levels = c('NSCLC','LUAD','LUSC')))
rownames(annotation_row) <- rownames(data) 
p1 <- pheatmap(mat = mat, border_color = 'black', color = colorRampPalette(c( "white", "#BC3C29"))(130),cluster_rows = F, cluster_cols = F, show_rownames = T, show_colnames = T, 
               annotation_row = annotation_row, annotation_colors = annColors, gaps_row = cumsum(table(annotation_row$Disease)), display_numbers = TRUE,  number_format = "%d", 
               fontsize_number = 15,number_color = "black",angle_row = 180,cellwidth = 30,cellheight = 30, width = 10, height = 10)
ggsave(filename = 'Figure 3D.pdf',p1 ,width = 6,height = 6)
